source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer FROM text_search(qs, 'second') order by score desc LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                              |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: text_search(qs, Utf8("second")).id, text_search(qs, Utf8("second")).answer                                            |
|               |   Sort: text_search(qs, Utf8("second")).score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=4                                                           |
|               |     Projection: text_search(qs, Utf8("second")).id, text_search(qs, Utf8("second")).answer, text_search(qs, Utf8("second")).score |
|               |       TableScan: text_search(qs, Utf8("second")) projection=[answer, id, score]                                                   |
